Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:23:02.16,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}是谁淋着雨 悄悄颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:07.38,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(200,200)}迷失森林 靠近天空
